# ArgoCD Application Patterns

## Bootstrap Applications
- Root Application manages cluster configuration deployment
- Use `clusters/overlays/<cluster-name>` as source path
- Set `destination.namespace: argocd` for bootstrap apps

## Application Structure
- `spec.source.path` - Git repository path to deploy from
- `spec.destination.namespace` - Target namespace in cluster
- `spec.syncPolicy.automated` - Enable automatic syncing

## Common Fields
- `repoURL` - Git repository URL
- `targetRevision` - Git branch/tag to track
- `project` - ArgoCD project for organization

## Best Practices
- Use semantic versioning for targetRevision
- Enable self-healing with `selfHeal: true`
- Set appropriate prune policies for cleanup
